title: Peach Lattice Pie
ingredients: ['310g plain flour', '3 tablespoons caster sugar', '1 teaspoon salt', '225g margarine', '1 egg', '60ml cold water', '1.3kg fresh peaches - peeled, stones removed and sliced', '60ml lemon juice', '180ml orange juice', '110g butter', '400g caster sugar', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1 tablespoon cornflour', '1 tablespoon caster sugar', '15g butter, melted']
